comments: Young (CHI) makes marginal contact to the body of Vucevic (ORL) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) makes contact with LaVine's (CHI) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Young (CHI) makes contact to the body of Anthony (ORL) at the start of his drive that affects his SQBR.
LaVine (CHI) places an arm against Vucevic's (ORL) back during the rebound, but does not extend into him and the contact during his putback attempt is marginal.
Fournier (ORL) makes clean contact with ball during LaVine's (CHI) driving shot attempt.  Any contact with LaVine's hand on the ball is considered incidental.
LaVine (CHI) makes contact to Fourner's (ORL) arm that affects his SQBR.
LaVine (CHI) reaches in and makes marginal contact with Fournier's (ORL) arm as he throws the errant pass.
Fournier (ORL) makes contact to LaVine's (CHI) right arm during his jump shot attempt.
Young (CHI) makes contact to the body of Anthony (ORL) on the drive that affects his SQBR.
Vucevic (ORL) makes marginal contact to the arm of LaVine (CHI) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Fournier (ORL) picks up his dribble and Temple (CHI) gets two hands on the ball and briefly dislodges it and Fournier legally regains possession.
Temple (CHI) reaches in and makes contact to Fournier's (ORL) arm as ORL is signaling for a timeout and officials grant the timeout.
Temple (CHI) commits a take foul on Vucevic (ORL).
